<br />\n絕左育<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wink.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4d6c4c35ac3831c54cd0e3233b7aaa3ea2ddec24","tid":459440,"uid":126766,"like":106,"dislike":0,"score":106,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T06:04:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/11/08/140421_0210250f50f022c8987c804e14c04fa3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F11%2F08%2F140421_0210250f50f022c8987c804e14c04fa3.jpg&h=20d50045&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n出街<br />\nFing曬尾<br />\n好開心<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30e2b2cd0a6fbd3da8f3aa22a3d99694a94d1e5a","tid":459440,"uid":4972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T06:06:06.000Z","msg":"笑晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee32f944d2676c1d641bd8d69228ae5451090655","tid":459440,"uid":132896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T06:07:46.000Z","msg":"好得意"},{"pid":"089d0bdc95ea262d16b59661c5d99049985b1b4c","tid":459440,"uid":29902,"like":35,"dislike":0,"score":35,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T06:08:48.000Z","msg":"諗起之前有日係屋企<br />\n無啦啦有隻狗係條走廊行<br />\n行到我屋企門口 之後又走開<br />\n咁我知道隔離左右無人養<br />\n就開門跟住佢 睇下佢行去邊<br />\n之後見佢係樓梯到坐<br />\n知道佢走失左 之後捉佢返屋企先 佢又勁乖完全無反抗<br />\ncall個養狗fd過黎幫手<br />\n之後帶埋隻狗去獸醫到照晶片<br />\n點知照唔到<br />\n後尾帶隻狗玩左陣 屙下尿咁<br />\n印左疊尋狗主啟示周圍貼<br />\n返到屋企樓下就見到狗主又貼緊尋狗啟示<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n之後狗主就比左500蚊我<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"351ce02d0ce9e4e6efd1b8204ecfe386fa3573c5","tid":459440,"uid":67976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-11-08T06:09:15.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/norma